channel.title: Devolopment team needed
channel.description:
Hello and Thank You for choosing this topic
I am not new to coding but i do need assistance a good server cant be done alone unless you are valentino lol. I am trying to make a server and i need some help from coders who are looking for a fun little project to work on with me. I have chosen to use Valentino and rene's Rune Fusion because i'm a fan of project insanity but the original insanity was kind of messy. There are still lots of bugs on Rune Fusion and things that can be done so i need some help from some of you. I come from deltascape coding so all this is sort of new to me so bare with me on the coding i have gotten some stuff done but not a lot! Here is my current position list
Owner - Zachary (me) Co Owner - open Main source Coder - open Source coder - open Main Client coder - open client coder - open Website design - ( cant really be done until i can get a .org but you can still apply for future ) Open
I am not looking for mods and admins i already have some respectable players for that i'm strictly looking for a development team not a maintain my server for me team. I will be helping code i am not asking people to code for me I'm still doing little things now that i know how to do from delta.
If you would like to join RuneJection please use the following template
Name - Age - Location - Position wanted - Why - your goal to achieve when helping - ( if you strictly want to try to make money put that if you want to help become then #1 server put that )
Thank-You for reading and lay off the flaming ill bake you all cookies and e-mail you them
